stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> Submitted: Form submitted
    Submitted --> Rejected: Validation failed
    Rejected --> Draft: User corrects data
    Submitted --> Duplicate: Email already exists
    Duplicate --> Draft: User changes email
    Submitted --> Approved: Validation passed
    Approved --> Persisted: Saved to database
    Persisted --> [*]
